<div id="node-205" class="node node-library">


  <h2><a href="../../library/chinafaqs-enhanced-bilateral-cooperation" title="ChinaFAQs: Enhanced Bilateral Cooperation">ChinaFAQs: Enhanced Bilateral Cooperation</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Posted by ChinaFAQs on Oct 22, 2009</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <a href="../../library/chinafaqs-enhanced-bilateral-cooperation" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-linked imagecache-news-image_linked"><img src="../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/ChinaFAQs&#32;Enhanced&#32;Bilateral&#32;Cooperation&#32;v2.png" alt="" title="" width="93" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image"/></a>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-library-file">
      <div class="field-label">Library File:&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <div class="filefield-file"><img class="filefield-icon field-icon-application-pdf"  alt="application/pdf icon" src="../../sites/all/modules/filefield/icons/application-pdf.png" /><a href="../../files/chinainfo/ChinaFAQs_Enhanced_Bilateral_Cooperation.pdf" type="application/pdf; length=309346">ChinaFAQs_Enhanced_Bilateral_Cooperation.pdf</a></div>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p>U.S.-China cooperation on climate change mitigation has taken a variety of forms, with different goals and structures.  Reviewed below are some of the recent fora for bilateral dialogue and collaboration.</p>
  </div>
<div class="clear-block">
    	<div class="readmore"> <a href="../../library/chinafaqs-enhanced-bilateral-cooperation">Read more</a> </div>
