<div id="node-195" class="node node-library">


  <h2><a href="../../library/wri-china-united-states-and-climate-change-challenge" title="WRI: China, the United States, and the Climate Change Challenge">WRI: China, the United States, and the Climate Change Challenge</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Posted by ChinaFAQs on Oct 22, 2009</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <a href="../../library/wri-china-united-states-and-climate-change-challenge" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-linked imagecache-news-image_linked"><img src="../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/china_united_states_climate_change_challenge-1.png" alt="" title="" width="93" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image"/></a>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-library-file">
      <div class="field-label">Library File:&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <div class="filefield-file"><img class="filefield-icon field-icon-application-pdf"  alt="application/pdf icon" src="../../sites/all/modules/filefield/icons/application-pdf.png" /><a href="../../files/chinainfo/china_united_states_climate_change_challenge.pdf" type="application/pdf; length=298260">china_united_states_climate_change_challenge.pdf</a></div>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p>A new WRI report, <a href="http://www.wri.org/publication/china-united-states-climate-change-challenge">China, the United States, and the Climate Change Challenge</a> discusses the successes and challenges to effective regulation in China, outlining the major advances made in implementing effective energy efficiency programs in the past several years. These include targeted programs for both large and small enterprises, specific goals for government officials, and the development of energy statistics infrastructure. It also addresses U.S.</p>
  </div>
<div class="clear-block">
    	<div class="readmore"> <a href="../../library/wri-china-united-states-and-climate-change-challenge">Read more</a> </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clear-block">
    <div class="meta">
