          <div class="links"><ul class="links inline"><li class="node_read_more first last"><a href="../../library/wri-china-united-states-and-climate-change-challenge" title="Read the rest of WRI: China, the United States, and the Climate Change Challenge.">Read more</a></li>
</ul></div>
