  <h2><a href="../../library/current-and-recent-us-china-climate-and-energy-cooperation-projects" title="Current and Recent U.S.-China Climate and Energy Cooperation Projects">Current and Recent U.S.-China Climate and Energy Cooperation Projects</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Posted by ChinaFAQs on Oct 20, 2009</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
